the one the best things life has to offer is the EnJoY that pops up on my microwave after i hit the popcorn bag is done. the trick to get it to say that though is you really have to hit the popcorn one-touch button. my buttery fingers are sticking to my keyboard on top of it; but i still am enjoying it. i always used to eat butter popcorn, but then  i stoped for two years with all popcorn in general. Then in the 9th grade i had an older friend who only ate (pause as the other half of the bag is in my mouth) non-buttered, plain popcorn. she enjoyed this, so i ate popcorn again, her way, nonbuttered and plain. to this day i think of her when i see unbuttered,super plain popcorn. then for some reason i picked up the superbuttered popcorn habit again. im not friends i suppose you could say with her anymore either. but now i can appresate(spelling on that???) the enjoy thing also, which i never did before or after the plain popcorn episode. does anyone follow me on my popcorn theory???

and reading has made me done some thinking; i really dont even know what but i believe im trying to dig up something in the past.i was going thorough a not a former friend, but i suppose a friend from a while ago entries. and i remember when she wrote her first one and that was her junior year and my freshmen. I think back to then and its so long ago but then again that was my only other highschool ish experience in a way since iwas locked up my 10th grade year. its almost as if im still picking up from that year, the end of my freshmen but now im only a junior and 16. like i dont know exacatly how to word what i want to say. i dont even know what mad me go back. my  friend jessie wiped out one particular cd that my friend and  i used to listen to NON-stop and it kinda freaked me out. i remember dancing around her room to these songs freshly just high. i remember it like yesterday and i was retartedly high but i still rememeber. andn ow it brings me back to now; i can only visit this past in my memories and no where else. im no longer anything like i was back then but i dont know who i am. i feel since i got out of that place im still trying to pick (insert pause of time here cos i just realized that i put hairdye in my hair and its been like a hour.)(back)something out. i think thought maybe i need to try out still living the status quo high school life as much as i dont want to. maybe im trying to move to fast to get away from it but maybe i need it to get from one place to another. i sure many would agree with me on this. i have to go through the toutrue of it all cos thats just how it is. though im not usually theone to go for things of just how they are. 

my friend had the same bond with trees that i have at this age and i read through her justafcations at 16 and i couldnt agree anymore; today her views are different and maybe ill be there in my future. i admire her, as i always have (maybe almost like an oldersiste)to this day; i want to almost go the same direction with my life the whole college thing as her; but then again i dont want to. i dont think ill be done  partying when i turn 18 but only merly start as another friend of mine who turned 18. these two friends are the same age but took totally different paths in life. i sit here comparing and trying to figure out which one i will fall in. i think though the best bet for me is just to let go of it all and let maybe my soul find its own way. maybe my heart needs to lead me instead of my head. i mean for all i know i could be a mom at 18 and not chose either of those( NOT implying anything). 

and one last thing; what dents my  uprise is that i love my downfall.

so as this songs says, we all have to die sometime. Nice realty check eh? my tiny head hurts. Stress. Devon. Death. Love. Lust. Hate. Passion. life.. dreams i believe hold some type of wisdom. I believe. I had a bad trip. I cheated with someones boyfriend. I smoked. I rode the waves. I rode the rides. I picked gum out of my hair. Everything was smooth. I had a best friend. I had breath. aw! hm, if she was so "over" this, why would she devote a whole page to me? i wonder; but thats all i can do. I'm not proud of what i did but, like i said before, im not sorry at that either. As for being in common, we became friends before we smoked 2gether so in all fact we must have had SOMETHING in common.And if when i asked her was our friendship stronger then weed, she agreed that it was. In fact a lie on her part. i wish she would go ahead and call my mum. Ive told her everything, i have nothing to hide. Also, im not pushing anyone away. The only ones i am are my parents which is undoubtfully understandable. Im not going to justif myself in this cos i dont have to. Like i said to Sharif. As for her little advice in this unpresident war : Beauty is in the Eye of the Beholder. I am beautiful in my own way and so are you.i am at peace with myself at last. I dont hold the key to the locks in life, but i will somehow break though them. And as for trying so hard, What for? i will not know any of you in three years. I will be fully free for the lies and the greed of others in this town. But now, the closest thing to that is going to europe for the summer :D As for me thinking you have a problem lady, thats left up for me to ponder. I have my own reasons as to why so. As in company in rehab, im leaving in 5weeks. Whats the point? As now to this sentence, i'm saying my final goodbye. We had our times and all in done. I hope you ripp though life as a jagged knife you've become. So long. P. eace L. ove U. nity R. espect One last thing, i have suscessfuly recieved my tickets back to greenday/blink tour-- i might have a ponteniol comer but shes not postive, if anyone is up for it, please do come towards. :D

so, im not sorry for what i did. How could i be? helpless im not. I dont speak of the devil. We were just what our names meant. We budded, lived, and died away. Miss the sweet aroma, i will. Never forget what light was bought in. Hope and dream, but not of me anymore. Live everything to death. Forget your past. Rise upon your highest toes. Fight the demons of the cycle; just dont get lost in who you are. This is drop of salt water for you. Its made its journy down my flesh. Let it dry up just as a past. Just dont forget, i'll always love you, eskimo.

I want to be rapped in silk linins and thrown over a cliff. Every so often just sit down and think. Think about where your going. I wish someone had given me that advice a long time ago. But, thats the past. You are the future. ramble ramble ramble on; I dont know who i am. I've lost myself in the mase of lines and dots. POP! goodnight. Hope and dream all you want, you will never get it. NEVER. Be careful in what you do; dont write a suidice note. Be open. Inhale the beauty that will kill one day.Pass a rock. Flick a ciggerate.Sniff that line. It will do you good; for the least time. Remeber that blue is the color of death, not black. Red is the light that used to be in all of us. But now, its all downward and around the coner of your path. Click, click, Click i am gone.

god, what a good week. i need this. i need to smoke. And i did. Actully way to much in one week. But yet again, like i said, it was a really good week. I wont get into details cos that would take up half the fucking day, but it also was somewhat of a funny week. Just plain funny, and good, of course.

So, now im sitting here with a green mask stuck on my face. It feels tingy :o)  <-- i like that face, heehz. But back to what Im thinking, yesterday man, yessterday was amazing. I smoked so much. I dont think i can begin to count. I went to yasi's, and suppiled munchies which cost me $60. Fucking food prices. So then we smoked my weed and rolled a joint. I brought about $60 worth of shit too.mwahhaha go me. So we smoked. Then we smoked some more and then, WE SMOKED JUST INCASE we didnt smoke enough before. But then a bit later on we smoked. So it was good. So then linday and christina lee come to yasi's. Linday was a kind hearted soul and walked me down to the highschool where i was supposed to be picked up. I havnt gotten around to telling my mother i quit the play so she thinks im still going to practices. It all works out. So my mum gets there but before she did, we came up to a plan: we would go back to my home, then eat, then go to lindays then back to yasi's then smoke again. It somewhat worked out. It worked out to the part where we got back to yasi's. We stayed for a few mintues. She was sleeping, burnt and being kinda bichty towards us. (no offence or anything man, i still luv ya) So then chris stayed and then linday i went down and walked to metro plants. We were hoping WEED see jeff and pete. Pete wasnt there, but jeffy was. So we begged him to get us stuff to smoke. Lindays didnt smoke all day and i was just starting to come down so i need something to pick me up again. So we just waited around and planted flowers in pots for jeff. haha i actully enjoyed that but its funny when you are high. ohh boy.. haha newayz so then my mum calls me on my cellie and was like WHERE THE FUCK ARE YOU?>! im like eh, metro and then i make up this laborious excuse to why i was there and not watching dvds at lindays.. so shes like im picking you up. Im like uh ok. so i tell lindays to come over like later on to sleep over. But i have spoken to her since. But newayz, i get home put my bag down in my room and leave to go online and make plans for the later part of the night. This is where it gets interesting...

My mother had gone though my bag.I should have none this.Shes maybe almost does it everyday day with my bag and room.She thinks i dont know. God, damnit then she wonders why i lie to her and why we have no trust. Shes always screaming at me she has no trust in me but like what the fuck?? how amm i supposed to trust you! Trust happens to be a toway think you know. but yet again in my mother's eyes, that doesnt belong....on with it.. She found my bowl, my cigg fliter which may i say could be used for j's or blunts, and two condoms. Why i was carring condoms, i have no fucking clue. I just had them from a very long time ago.They just happened to creep into my bag. Or maybe, maybe my subconsence was hoping to get some ass. But, like yea right. Thats another entry. But back to the story, she was somewhat pissed and was like jasmina what the hell what the hell. That was the end of it. Nothing more of it. Im not punished or anything. <---that is the interesting part of the story. For me, at least.

So later on the night was good too. My friend came and picked me up at like 12.It was really funny*even to me* that i was so burnt i had a problem trying to walk out the door without making any noise. My parents didnt no i was going of course. but it was quit amuzing seen. lol  We smoked straight untill 3. God it was great. Then i came home and slept. :D

So i also have come to desided that bowls are bad luck for me. At least ones that i buy. I think its just cursed upon me. I think im going to stick to the soda can. Works greatly and you get a drink outta it. What better could that be? besides its cheaper so you have more money for weed. Think about it. NO hassle with screens, or cleaning out you bowl, you dont have to pay like $30 for a really good one, can get they almost anywhere in the world, and its not werid to go buy one just incase your parents find it! haha!

hmm so i think im pretty much done. im going to go like try to get this mask off my face now. its been on to long cos i was writing in here. meh!

href="http://www.streea-davis.com/element.htm">
Want To Know Which Element You Are?

Stuck between the sky and the ground, you lack the sudden impulse that Air has but are unable to root yourself down like Earth. Though you have troubles finishing projects, people can depend on you for the most part (even if it means pulling a few all-nighters). On the plus side, you are extremely adaptable and thus can adjust to any situation. Sure, you might not like it, but it doesn't weigh you down.

Best Match: Fire, just enough 'oomph' to keep your interest.
Worst Match: Spirit, you'll be out the door before they make up their minds.
